  "id" : "api/core/ContentChildDecorator",
  "title" : "ContentChildDecorator",
  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"contentchilddecorator\">ContentChildDecorator</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\">@angular/core</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/core/ContentChildDecorator\" class=\"code-anchor\">ContentChildDecorator</a> } from <a href=\"api/core\">'@angular/core'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/src/metadata/di.ts#L197-L236\">core/src/metadata/di.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<h2 id=\"interface-overview\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"15ffnfvjx5orhxzfayretyfy4\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>接口概览</h2>\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/ContentChildDecorator\" class=\"code-anchor\">ContentChildDecorator</a> { \n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ContentChildDecorator#call\">(selector: Type&lt;any&gt; | Function | string, opts?: {...}): any</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ContentChildDecorator#new\">new (selector: Type&lt;any&gt; | Function | string, opts?: {...}): ContentChild</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cijgd55okwmt5u2411y894hyy\">ContentChild 装饰器/构造函数的类型。</p>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-members\">\n  <h2 id=\"members\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e62kgm2ztk7rgk6auybfiv91o\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>成员</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"call\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">(selector: <a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a>&lt;any&gt; | Function | string, opts?: {\n    read?: any;\n}): any</code-example>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"br1ewgrlutuwt6w0156ovh7ee\">你可以使用 ContentChild 从内容 DOM 中获取与选择器匹配的第一个元素或指令。如果内容 DOM 发生变化，并且新的子元素与选择器匹配，则该属性将被更新。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2mv0w7n7tz5ea75fcgwsnpzqt\">在调用 <code>ngAfterContentInit</code> 之前设置的内容查询。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"958p250s4a4gqxdqtti9sbuqo\"><strong>元数据属性</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6ixorlow9hdb02vbe8pe45lr\"><strong>selector</strong> - 用于查询的指令类型或名称。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bmwywdwx3enmkfhol5kmlqcqt\"><strong>read</strong> — 从查询的元素中读取不同的令牌。</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1as6sssxkbpwanrxvy471wt78\">让我们看一个例子：</p>\n<code-example>\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>, <a href=\"api/core/ContentChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ContentChild</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({selector: 'pane'})\nexport class Pane {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>() id: string;\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'tab',\n  template: `\n    &lt;div&gt;pane: {{pane?.id}}&lt;/div&gt; \n  `\n})\nexport class Tab {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/ContentChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ContentChild</a>(Pane) pane: Pane;\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'example-app',\n  template: `\n    &lt;tab&gt;\n      &lt;pane id=\"1\" *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"shouldShow\"&gt;&lt;/pane&gt;\n      &lt;pane id=\"2\" *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"!shouldShow\"&gt;&lt;/pane&gt;\n    &lt;/tab&gt;\n    \n    &lt;button (click)=\"toggle()\"&gt;Toggle&lt;/button&gt;\n  `,\n})\nexport class ContentChildComp {\n  shouldShow = true;\n\n  toggle() { this.shouldShow = !this.shouldShow; }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<p><strong>npm package</strong>: <code>@angular/core</code></p>\n\n  </div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"new\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">new (selector: <a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a>&lt;any&gt; | Function | string, opts?: {\n    read?: any;\n}): <a href=\"api/core/ContentChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ContentChild</a></code-example></div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/ContentChild\n - api/core/ContentChildDecorator#call\n - api/core/ContentChildDecorator#contentchilddecorator\n - api/core/ContentChildDecorator#description\n - api/core/ContentChildDecorator#interface-overview\n - api/core/ContentChildDecorator#members\n - api/core/ContentChildDecorator#new\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/Input\n - api/core/Type\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/src/metadata/di.ts#L197-L236\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\n-->"
